---
source: tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs
assertion: ee.query.v1 trust and redaction query-file filters use policy-aware selection instead of silent acceptance
schema:
  query_file: ee.query.v1
  filters:
    trust: ee.query.filters.trust.v1
    redaction: ee.query.filters.redaction.v1
contracts:
  - trust.minClass filters candidates by minimum trust class
  - trust.excludeClasses removes disallowed trust classes
  - trust.requirePosture validates supported trust postures
  - redaction.policy=respect is accepted and preserves redaction behavior
  - redaction.policy=bypass is policy-denied without elevated permission
  - redaction.allowCategories filters on stable redaction reason codes without leaking secret content
evidence:
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_trust_min_class_succeeds
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_redaction_respect_succeeds
  - tests/conformance/query_v1_matrix.rs::matrix_redaction_allow_categories_filters_secret_reasons
  - src/cli/mod.rs::validate_trust_object
  - src/cli/mod.rs::validate_redaction_object
  - eidetic_engine_cli-vpqq
